oai_dc:dc.dc:title: FSU Men's Basketball Game Contact Sheet
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Mittan, J. Barry
oai_dc:dc.dc:publisher: Heritage Protocol, Florida State University, Tallahassee, Florida.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photographs from Florida State University student, J. Barry Mittan, class of 1971 (BS, Psychology). While a student he was a photographer for numerous FSU publications, as well as the Athletic Department and the FSU Flying High Circus. These photographs are from his student photographer portfolio and are a part of the J. Barry Mittan Photograph Collection, 1965-1971 (HP-2008-020).
Labeled CS 101. B/W; aprox. 8x10 (Accession No. HP-2008-020).
